    "target": "url:http://localhost:18095",
    "readOnly": false,
    "note": "Reuses FIXTURES.qrPayload. Chains steps with {{steps.<name>.<field>}}. This flow is where the ops BFF once faked schemeTxnRef/approval — scrubFields keeps the volatile ref out of the diff while still comparing the real values.",
